{"tid":2014584,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[東網] 新病例響重大警號　袁國勇：若續現本地個案或須暫緩復課","createTime":"2020-05-13T06:20:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-13T06:27:09.000Z","uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"a5d9efd45a50faefafb2eaf981e6b7552e689c28","tid":2014584,"uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T06:20:49.000Z","msg":"[東網] 新病例響重大警號 袁國勇：若續現本地個案或須暫緩復課<br />\n05月13日(三) 13:55更新<br />\n<br />\n消息指一名居於荃灣梨木樹邨的66歲女子初步確診新冠肺炎，可能成為香港二十多日以來首宗本地確診個案。港大微生物學系講座教授袁國勇今日(13日)表示，有關個案令防疫工作響起重大警號，他認為應即時全面加強檢測，全港每日最少要檢驗7500個樣本才足夠。他更認為如果更多本地個案出現，或許需要暫緩復課安排。<br />\n<br />\n(已節錄)<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200513/bkn-20200513083626804-0513_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20200513%2Fbkn-20200513083626804-0513_00822_001.html&d=RJ6DAKdT%2BAkj0rfdhPz9NSWRWsFhQrZK9M853DAdSZ8%3D&h=6330c723\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200513/bkn-20200513083626804-0513_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"cee74a43ff1b61d4ae2d2a4b4329dfb954a34eff","tid":2014584,"uid":340088,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T06:24:02.000Z","msg":"又燈唔爆"},{"pid":"8037f53ff3eaf469ec2f40f1291dc5c37dd98783","tid":2014584,"uid":2959,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T06:27:09.000Z","msg":"wfh未"}]}